{"tid":447613,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)自殺特攻 訪嚇/逃出絕命鎮 原子殺姬","createTime":"2017-10-25T12:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T17:08:50.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f33ca74793428383455d92f269b0116635467184","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WPolAX35BWK%2FJrna%2Boau154%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ca383827\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V台入佢主頁睇先比較順<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WPolAX35BWK%2FJrna%2Boau154%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5c0775be\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> dailymotion執柒左 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://ok.ru/videoembed/342649413317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fok.ru%2Fvideoembed%2F342649413317&d=WPolAX35BWK%2FJrna%2Boau154%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=44d9c6a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ok.ru/videoembed/342649413317</a>全MON版 測試中<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/96/Suicide_Squad_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F96%2FSuicide_Squad_Poster.jpg&h=0fcadd8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/60/Get_Out_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F60%2FGet_Out_Poster.jpg&h=364dd882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://movie.yahoo-leisure.hk/assets/poster/AtomicBlond6021120832104019258_380x560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovie.yahoo-leisure.hk%2Fassets%2Fposter%2FAtomicBlond6021120832104019258_380x560.jpg&h=b3bf6b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.經過超人之死的浩劫後，隸屬政府秘密組織「天眼局」的女官員阿曼達&middot;華勒，決定組織一支由多名極度危險罪犯所組成的「X特遣部隊」，來為美國政府承擔高風險任務，確保有人能夠阻止下一個侵害社會的強大敵人。華勒到美夢監獄招收了多名惡名昭彰的超級罪犯：槍法精準的精英殺手「死亡射手」、瘋狂及致命的前精神科醫生「哈莉&middot;奎茵」、能夠召喚火焰的前洛杉磯幫派分子「燄魔」、善用迴旋鏢的澳洲盜賊「迴旋鏢隊長」、因為基因突變而擁有鱷魚外表和習性的野蠻罪犯「殺手鱷」、以及善用繩索的職業傭兵「繩鬼」，讓他們全部聽從由政府指派的軍官上校瑞克&middot;佛萊格的指揮，而每個人的脖子裏都被注射一顆小型奈米炸彈作為保險措施，以防止他們在任務中造反或是逃跑..<br />\n<br />\n2.一位名叫安德烈&middot;海沃斯的黑人年輕小夥於深夜在郊區裏散步，和他的女友在通電話時突然被一輛白色汽車跟蹤，當他試圖遠離汽車時，卻被車中的一名蒙面人弄昏後塞進車中帶走。<br />\n過了幾個月，一位黑人攝影師克里斯&middot;華盛頓陪他的白人女友蘿絲&middot;阿米蒂奇開車前往蘿絲位於郊區小鎮的老家度週末，而克里斯一直認為他的膚色問題很可能會受到她的家人指點。到達後，克里斯接見了蘿絲的父母和哥哥，神經外科醫生迪恩、心理醫生蜜西、以及摔跤愛好者傑瑞米..<br />\n<br />\n3.冷戰時期，英國軍情六處的首席女特務露溫保杜(Lorraine Broughton)(查理絲花朗 飾)，向來無所不用其極完成不可能的任務，是MI6中最致命狠勁的間諜。她的最新任務是單人匹馬前往動蕩不安的柏林，追尋一份不翼而飛的間諜名單。露溫在柏林受四面埋伏，必須與情報探員大衛珀斯(David Percival)(占士麥艾禾 飾)合作，找出一線生機。這場諜戰危機足以威脅整個西方世界，第三次世界大戰一觸即發..<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=WPolAX35BWK%2FJrna%2Boau154%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2fe9752b\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=WPolAX35BWK%2FJrna%2Boau154%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=99d00f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b042075a62d7fe968f0fd539220f3b385d368d1","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d4172c112125c663ec19d062c18795a603dfce","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ea2adf194664d608fe82c3843117a36dcf33fb","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9078e18ba4e03a15adb13cfc52ead559ea18900b","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515892bdcd61a7c50046ba47496684554f024f47","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796979dd1b695539baca172493f1a68a611152fc","tid":447613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}